{"type":null,"faqId":40549,"title":"如何用Huawei HiLink进行迅雷绑定（迅雷账号与路由器绑定）？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:#00a0e9;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s4{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>迅雷绑定是将您的个人迅雷账号与路由器进行绑定，这样，当您在公司或出门在外时，就能使用迅雷远程功能，直接“命令”家里的路由器开始下载，并将文件保存到路由器外接的USB存储设备中，回家就能直接观影。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">进行迅雷绑定前，请做如下准备工作</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">&gt;  </span><span>您需要有一个迅雷账号。如果还没有，可以先在迅雷官网上进行注册申请。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">&gt;  </span><span>路由器需插上USB存储设备（推荐使用移动硬盘，读写速度更快）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请按照以下步骤进行绑定</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>手机连接路由器的Wi-Fi。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>打开Huawei HiLink。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击右上角点击右上角设置图标 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137603\" style=\"width:0.19791667in;height:0.19791667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">互联网应用 &gt; 远程下载</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">远程登录</span><span>”注册一个华为账号，或用已有的华为账号登录。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>成功登录华为账号后，在迅雷绑定页面中输入您的迅雷账号和密码（若没有，需在迅雷官网上注册申请）。点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">登录并授权</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">授权</span><span>”即允许Huawei HiLink访问迅雷服务。此时，您将看到路由器的硬盘存储空间以及“</span><span class=\"s4\">新建任务</span><span>”按钮，即表示迅雷绑定成功。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137604\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>   </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137605\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9395833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137606\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137607\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137608\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9395833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137609\" style=\"width:2.3097222in;height:3.9361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137610\" style=\"width:2.30625in;height:3.9361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137611\" style=\"width:2.3020833in;height:3.942361in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5896","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768547000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":15,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}